1. Look at the *.url files
2. Go to the NEWS page in the *.url file
3. Write down the the latest version number
4. Create a directory in the format:

cdd-<version>
uniprot-<version>

for example:
cdd-2011-05/
uniprot-2011-08/

5. cd into these directories and download
all of the non-NEWS items the appropriate *.url file.
